Figure 4: Districts and Electricity Grid in Ethiopia

Olsa Berani

Objective

This notebook replicates Figure 4: Districts and Electricity Grid in Ethiopia from Fried and Lagakos (2021) as part of the take-home assignment on spatial data visualization using vector data in economics.

Data

  • District boundaries: GADM (administrative level 2)
  • Electricity grid: OpenStreetMap, extracted using Overpass Turbo

Replication
